overview: After a night at the bar, a guy invites a girl home to see his angelﬁsh. Over the course of just a few minutes, a promising connection is cut off and a ﬁsh is no longer a ﬁsh. A taut exchange that examines acceptable behavior in dating and mating rituals.

production_companies.name: Australian Film Television and Radio School (AFTRS)

title: Angelfish
